New map trikz_uproar2 


Uproar2 introduces you to new techs at each stage, and you will see many unusual things for the first time. At first, each stage may seem complicated and not comparable to the tier displayed, but it's not, it's worth playing a little more and understanding and stability will come over time. ENJOY :3


Tier: 4 - 10 (1 stage + 1 tier)
Map: 7 stages, 1 rbb, 3 solos
SB: 1 ("autoboost" on hard/old version of last stage from map)


link - https://gamebanana.com/mods/514961



Special thanks @Sulliven, he made some new techs
& Bits project & all testers
